OL,3,CRetail sales make subdued recovery as
OL,4,Cwashout summer dries up
OL,6,FThe late arrival of summer returned
OL,7,Fretail sales to growth ` boosted by
OL,8,Fconsumers buying clothing and beauty
OL,9,Fproducts in preparation for the
OL,10,Fholidays, figures show.
