OL,3,CRetail sales make subdued recovery as
OL,4,Cwashout summer dries up
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The late arrival of British
OL,8,Fsunshine led to a better month for
OL,9,Fsummer clothing and health and beauty
OL,10,Fproducts as shoppers prepared for days
OL,11,Fout with friends and holidays away."
OL,13,FLinda Ellett, UK head of consumer,
OL,14,Fretail and leisure at KPMG, said:
OL,15,F"While summer staples, such as health,
OL,16,Fbeauty, and gardening products have
OL,17,Fhelped to drive retail sales growth
OL,18,Fboth online and in-store in July, the
OL,19,Fupturn is likely much less than
OL,20,Fretailers were hoping for at this key
OL,21,Ftime of the year.
